	<name>AppFuse Maven Plugin</name>
	<version>2.0.0-SNAPSHOT</version>
	<inceptionYear>2006</inceptionYear>
    <description>
        The appfuse-maven-plugin project is now part of the AppFuse project.  This plugin was originally
        created by Scott Ryan and began at Codehaus.  This plugin will be very useful for AppFuse developers and
        also users of AppFuse as a foundational application.  This plugin is used with Maven to generate source
        code from a database connection or existing model objects or Pojos.  The plugin is not fully functional,
        but it's now available with full checkouts of AppFuse.  It will remain isolated from the AppFuse build
        until it's ready for public consumption.
    </description>
